JSONExtract(mt_log_avail, 'filledDuration', 'Double') AS mt_log_avail_filled_duration,
JSONExtract(mt_log_avail, 'numAds', 'UInt32') AS mt_log_avail_num_ads,

JSONExtract(mt_log_avail_slate_ad, 'creativeUniqueId', 'String') AS mt_log_avail_slate_ad_creative_unique_id,
JSONExtract(mt_log_avail_slate_ad, 'transcodedAdDuration', 'UInt32') AS mt_log_avail_slate_ad_transcoded_ad_duration,
JSONExtract(mt_log_avail_slate_ad, 'uri', 'String') AS mt_log_avail_slate_ad_uri,

JSONExtractRaw(COALESCE(mt_log_vast_response, ''), 'vastAds')  as mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads,

JSONExtract(mt_log_vast_response, 'errors', 'String') AS mt_log_vast_response_errors,

JSONExtractRaw(mt_log_avail_creative_ads, 1) as theAd,

extractAll(mt_log_avail_creative_ads, '"uri":"([^"]*)"') AS test_uris,
extractAll(mt_log_avail_creative_ads, '"vastDuration":([^"]*)}') AS mt_log_avail_creative_ads_vast_duration_array,

extractAll(mt_log_avail_creative_ads, '"transcodedAdDuration":([^"]*),') AS mt_log_avail_creative_ads_transcoded_ad_duration_array,

JSONExtractRaw(COALESCE(mt_log_avail_creative_ads, ''), 'impression')  as test_impression_string,

extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"type":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_vast_media_files_type_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"uri":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_vast_media_files_uri_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"width":([^"]*)}') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_vast_media_files_width_array,



extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"uri":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_uri_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"duration":([^"]*),') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"adSystem":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_ad_ad_system_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"adTitle":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_ad_title_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"creativeAdId":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_creative_ad_id_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"creativeId":{"([^"]*)}') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_creative_id_array,
extractAll(mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads, '"vastAdId":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_vast_response_vast_ads_vast_ad_id_array,


JSONExtractRaw(COALESCE(mt_log_beacon_info, ''), 'headers')  as mt_log_beacon_info_headers,
extractAll(mt_log_beacon_info_headers, '"name":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_beacon_info_headers_name,
extractAll(mt_log_beacon_info_headers, '"value":"([^"]*)"') AS mt_log_beacon_info_headers_value_array,



arrayFlatten(
    arrayMap(
        x -> splitByString(
            '","',
            replaceRegexpAll(
                replaceRegexpAll(
                    JSONExtractRaw(x, 'trackingEvents'),
                    '\\[\\"', ''
                ),
                '\\"\\]', ''
            )
        ),
        JSONExtractArrayRaw(mt_log_avail_creative_ads)
    )
) AS mt_log_avail_creative_ads_tracking_events_array,

arrayMap(
  x -> JSONExtract(x, 'Map(String, Array(String))'), 
  extractAll(
    mt_log_avail_creative_ads, 
      '"trackingEvents":([^\}]*\})'
  )
) AS mt_log_avail_creative_ads_tracking_events_arrays,



--JSONExtract(mt_log_avail_creative_ads_tracking_events_array, '"impression":"([^"]*)"') AS test_impression_string,




*
FROM {STREAM}
